volume (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of per-application volume control tool
  * System tray integration with mouse wheel support
  * Real-time PulseAudio application discovery
  * Individual volume sliders for each audio application
  * Compact UI with minimal whitespace
  * Master volume control via scroll wheel over tray icon
  * Asynchronous PulseAudio processing for responsive UI
  * Memory leak fixes and code quality improvements
  * Floating-point precision in volume calculations
  * Named constants for better maintainability

 -- Chris Wage <cwage@quietlife.net>  Fri, 08 Aug 2025 12:00:00 +0000